Johannesburg City Municipality Seeking $134 Million Loan For Its Cash Flow

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-07-15T05:06:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-15/johannesburg-city-municipality-seeking-134-million-loan-for-its-cash-flow.html
The City of Johannesburg
Metropolitan Municipality is seeking 920 million rand ($134
million) in funds from banks to “mitigate cash flow mismatches
and to optimise the total cost of borrowing,” it said in an
advertisement in Business Day newspaper today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  